    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and let me tell you, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-loved and taken care of, so you can just hop in and go. Perfect for commutes or weekend getaways! I\u2019m looking for a smooth sale to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
