    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is powered by the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8, featuring eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior mechanical grip. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly remains within spec. The chassis features Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a carbon fiber roof for a lower center of gravity. This is a well-sorted example with consistent compression across all cylinders, showing minor cosmetic patina expected of a driven enthusiast vehicle.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
