      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a sophisticated balance of performance and reliability. This automobile has been curated for the driver who demands mechanical integrity and a polished presentation without compromise. It exhibits consistent maintenance history and remains in an impressive state of preservation, ensuring a premium driving experience. We invite you to acquire a vehicle that exemplifies both quality engineering and enduring value.",
      "price": 36850.0,
