      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly in such great shape. It\u2019s been super well-maintained, runs smoothly, and the interior is still looking sharp and cozy. It\u2019s been a total joy to drive and is ready for its next adventure with a new owner. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable, clean car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Come by and see it for yourself\u2014I'd love to show you around it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
