    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered for acquisition is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine. This power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear, high-threshold power band peaking at an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, ensuring tactile engagement and superior corner-exit traction. The chassis has been maintained with a focus on structural integrity, including a recent subframe reinforcement inspection and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. While the exterior displays honest road-going patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the suspension kinematics remain sharp due to refreshed bushings and dampers. A recent valve clearance adjustment ensures the valvetrain operates with factory precision, making this an ideal candidate for the purist seeking a driver-focused M-car.",
